        "creator"
      ],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_158_world5"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_158_world5",
      "worldId": "world5",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "创造者",
      "dialogue": "「我是谁？」我问。\n\n「我是『一』。」他说，「也是『万』。」\n\n「我是开始，也是终结。」\n\n「我是...创造者。」",
      "background": "void",
      "characters": [
        "creator"
      ],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_159_world5"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_159_world5",
      "worldId": "world5",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "创造者",
      "dialogue": "「为什么...要把自己分裂？」\n\n创造者沉默了很久。\n\n「因为孤独。」他说，「绝对的孤独。」\n\n「我创造了所有世界，所有生命...但我无法参与。」\n\n「我是观察者，不是参与者。」",
      "background": "void",
      "characters": [
        "creator"
      ],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_160_world5"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_160_world5",
      "worldId": "world5",
      "type": "choice",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "真相揭露。你选择：",
